data.description: 2.626 acres with a combination cleared and wooded property located in Shady Oaks Estates subdivision in Montgomery County. Home is conveniently located within a mile from the Aggies Freeway (Hwy 249) and less than a block off FM 1486 Rd. Great opportunity to purchase acreage near all the amenities within just a few miles in any direction. This property can also be a great investment opportunity or build custom on your own lot. Zoned to Magnolia ISD.
